## 8. YOUR RIGHTS UNDER DPDP ACT, 2023

### 8.1 Right to Access

You can request a copy of all personal data we hold about you.

**How:** Email privacy@brandklip.com
**Format:** We'll provide as downloadable file (CSV, PDF, JSON)
**Response time:** 30 days
**Cost:** Free

---

### 8.2 Right to Correction

You can correct inaccurate or incomplete data.

**How:** 
- Update directly in Settings (name, email, phone, Instagram)
- Or email support@brandklip.com for help
**Response time:** Immediate (self-service) or 7 days (support)
**Examples:** Fix typo in name, update email, change phone

---

### 8.3 Right to Erasure ("Right to be Forgotten")

You can request deletion of your data, with exceptions.

**We can delete:**
- ✅ Your personal details (name, email, phone)
- ✅ Your profile information
- ✅ Your settings and preferences
- ✅ Your campaign history (after retention period)

**We must keep:**
- ⚠️ Tax records (7 years - legal requirement)
- ⚠️ Dispute data (until resolved)
- ⚠️ Anonymized analytics (cannot identify you)

**How:** Email privacy@brandklip.com or Settings → Delete Account

---

### 8.4 Right to Restrict Processing

You can limit how we use your data.

**Examples:**
- "Analytics only, no marketing"
- "Don't store usage data"
- "Email only, no WhatsApp"

**How:** Email privacy@brandklip.com or Settings → Privacy

---

### 8.5 Right to Data Portability

You can receive your data in machine-readable format.

**How:** Email privacy@brandklip.com
**Format:** CSV, JSON, or other structured format
**Response time:** 30 days
**Cost:** Free

---

### 8.6 Right to Object

You can opt-out of:
- Marketing emails: Click unsubscribe or Settings → Marketing
- Analytics tracking: Settings → Privacy → Opt out of analytics
- Personalized ads: Settings → Privacy → Disable personalization
- WhatsApp notifications: Settings → Notifications

---

### 8.7 Automated Decision-Making

BrandKlip does NOT use automated decisions for:
- ✅ Approving/rejecting Creators (humans review)
- ✅ Approving/rejecting videos (humans review)
- ✅ Determining payment amounts (contract-based)

Humans make all significant decisions affecting you.

