## 9. DATA SECURITY

### 9.1 Technical Safeguards

- **HTTPS/SSL:** All data in transit encrypted (https://)
- **Database encryption:** AES-256 at rest
- **Password hashing:** BCrypt (industry standard)
- **No plain text:** Sensitive data never stored plainly
- **Regular updates:** Security patches applied regularly

### 9.2 Access Controls

- **Employee access:** Limited to authorized personnel only
- **Confidentiality agreements:** All team members sign
- **Role-based access:** Finance sees payment data only, etc.
- **Activity logging:** Track who accesses what, when
- **No admin override:** Even admin can't see passwords

### 9.3 Security Testing

- **Regular audits:** Security review every quarter
- **Penetration testing:** External security experts test
- **Vulnerability scanning:** Automated scanning weekly
- **Bug bounty:** We reward security researchers who find issues

### 9.4 Data Breach Response

**If your data is breached:**

1. **Immediate:** We investigate and contain
2. **24 hours:** We notify you via email
3. **48 hours:** We notify authorities if required
4. **7 days:** We provide detailed breach report
5. **Guidance:** We help you protect your account

